show.description: Ek mysterious one-night stand, ek billionaire CEO, aur ek waitress jiske paas sirf ek memory hai. Aakhir uske bachche ka father kaun hai? Miranda ki life ban jaati hai ek emotional rollercoaster jab uska past uske saamne khada hota hai. Kya woh sach tak pahunch paayegi? Abhi dekhana shuru kijiye.
